277
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:36,720
No, I just…

278
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,360
Fine, I’m sorry.

279
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:39,920
I’m sorry.

280
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:41,360
