298
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:37,440
So I can keep up with everyone.

299
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:40,280
You’re ahead of everyone 
with your meatball joke.

300
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,920
You don’t need to be so close.

301
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:51,360
