323
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:19,480
See?

324
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:21,960
You don’t look surprised either.

325
00:21:27,560 --> 00:21:29,720
If you really fell for someone, 

326
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:33,480
