327
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:34,760
Right.

328
00:21:57,040 --> 00:21:59,840
Today is our day, Augar and August.

329
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:01,520
We will win every medal.

330
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:05,000
I’ll compete in every game you are in. 

331
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:07,360
