332
00:22:07,760 --> 00:22:08,960
You can compete in any games 
that you want.

333
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:11,800
I won’t join you. 
I’ll cheer on you from the sidelines.

334
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,600
But we are on different teams.

335
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:15,640
It’s okay.

336
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:17,160
I’ll cheer on the Red team.

337
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:19,080
I’ll be a spy.

338
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:21,160
Yay!

339
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,120
Let’s say this together.

340
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:33,200
Three.

341
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:35,480
Yay!

342
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:37,600
Yay!

343
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:41,200
Damn it. 
Why didn’t you wait until I finished?

344
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:46,000
Our timing is really off.

345
00:22:46,520 --> 00:22:47,240
Let’s go.

346
00:22:48,120 --> 00:22:48,600
