347
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:50,760
Let’s get our victory.

348
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:53,640
Yay!

349
00:23:12,840 --> 00:23:16,120
You can do it, Augar.

350
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:23,040
That’s good, Augar. Keep going.

351
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,360
I’ll show you what I got.

352
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:28,600
Two points.

353
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:31,000
Time’s up.

354
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:39,600
Is he kidding me?

355
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:55,640
Ko Song, you can do it. 
We are cheering you on.

356
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:57,120
Ko, go for it.

357
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,520
Come on.

358
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:02,040
The Red team is taking the lead.

359
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:08,240
- Come on. Faster. 
- The Blue team reaches the finish line.

360
00:24:15,520 --> 00:24:16,720
Are you okay?

361
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:19,720
Are you okay?

362
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:27,200
Kids, can you make way for me?

363
00:24:34,280 --> 00:24:34,960
Does it hurt?

364
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:36,840
A little.

365
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:39,120
I can’t put my weight on this foot.

366
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:44,800
You didn’t warm up before running, right?

367
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:46,280
No.

368
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,680
I was in a hurry.

369
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:52,040
A senior told me 
that an athlete from Grade 10 was sick.

370
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:53,160
So I had to take his place in the race.

371
00:24:54,320 --> 00:24:56,320
