397
00:26:18,360 --> 00:26:18,920
Are you okay?

398
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,480
I’m okay.

399
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:23,720
Go for it.

400
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:36,240
I’m fine.

401
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,240
- I’m fine. 
- You should rest.

402
00:26:37,560 --> 00:26:38,480
