436
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:09,360
The referee blows the final whistle.

437
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:13,240
The Red team beat the Yellow team by 3-2.

438
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:17,800
Well done, the Red team.

439
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:49,920
