475
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:30,160
Damn, I like you.

476
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:32,320
You are trying to be a hero.

477
00:31:34,040 --> 00:31:34,760
So what are you going to do?

478
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:38,640
Your mindset is so bullshit.

479
00:31:39,560 --> 00:31:40,120
What did you say?

480
00:31:41,080 --> 00:31:42,120
Didn’t you hear it?

481
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:44,400
