488
00:31:57,760 --> 00:31:59,840
Hey, let it go.

489
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,080
He’s just a nuisance.

490
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:02,880
Don’t have a problem with a school athlete.

491
00:32:03,040 --> 00:32:04,480
