495
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,440
You were ready to fight them.

496
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:23,840
Damn.

497
00:32:24,120 --> 00:32:26,000
I thought I would be hit by them. 

498
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:30,240
Thank you, Augar and August.

499
00:32:30,760 --> 00:32:32,560
