500
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:33,720
It’s not your fault.

501
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:36,080
Those seniors were crazy.

502
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:40,240
But I caused you a problem.

503
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:44,480
Buy us ice cream.

504
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:46,520
Sure.

505
00:32:47,040 --> 00:32:48,440
But I need to take a rain check.

506
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,160
I have to go home now.

507
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,480
What, Achi?

508
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:53,800
You need to buy it today.

509
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,280
You can go home later.

510
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:01,440
This is my house.

511
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:11,520
See you tomorrow.

512
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:13,320
See you.

513
00:33:13,320 --> 00:33:14,480
Thank you.

514
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:19,400
Damn!

515
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:22,880
Why didn’t he hire a bodyguard 
to accompany him 24/7?

516
00:33:23,280 --> 00:33:25,920
He told me that if I slept over at his house,

517
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:27,360
he would arrange a guest room for me.

518
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,000
I thought he was joking.

519
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,840
Damn!

520
00:33:37,560 --> 00:33:39,200
You did a great job today, Orange.

521
00:33:40,760 --> 00:33:41,920
It’s a sure thing.

522
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:45,000
Do you also play football?

523
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:45,840
I’ve never seen you play it before.

524
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:47,880
Sometimes.

525
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:49,480
But I don’t like it.

526
00:33:52,520 --> 00:33:55,360
Did you find what you like?

527
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:05,760
I like being with you.

528
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:09,720
What?

529
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:13,000
When I’m with you, 

530
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:15,000
I feel happiest.

531
00:34:16,200 --> 00:34:18,640
You are a safe zone for me.

532
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:24,200
Thanks.

533
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:32,480
What about you?

534
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,880
Do you like having me around?

535
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:39,120
Yeah.

536
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:41,760
But you annoy me sometimes.

537
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:43,920
Are you messing with me?

538
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:56,840
