How did you know that I’m smiling?

541
00:35:01,560 --> 00:35:02,440
Can you go faster?

542
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:04,000
I’m hungry. I want to go home.

543
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:05,120
Okay.

544
00:35:05,560 --> 00:35:06,400
You need to choose 

545
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:09,680
