546
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:17,200
My friend won the top spot today.

547
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:18,840
He won a gold medal.

548
00:35:21,200 --> 00:35:22,200
Let’s go.

549
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:35,440
