551
00:35:40,160 --> 00:35:40,840
I’m fine.

552
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:42,760
I’m not crippled.

553
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:47,400
Now, he knows how to talk back.

554
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:51,360
See you. I’m going in.

